<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="goodbye-n">goodbye <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌɡʊd'baɪ/    美 /ˌɡʊd'baɪ/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>告别：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Murray was at the port to <strong>wave goodbye</strong> to his friend.
默里在港口向他的朋友挥手告别。</p><footer>2012 山东改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sweeping the dust out of the house is a way of saying goodbye to old things and welcoming new things.
扫除房子的灰尘是辞旧迎新的一种方式。</p><footer>人教新必修③ – 1</footer></div></div>